(241, 'duT4030ECc', 'normal', NULL, 35, 24, 41, 131, NULL, 'Swiss-Made Auto Safety Master Opener by Kuhn Rikon', 'swiss-made-auto-safety-master-opener-by-kuhn-rikon-dut4030ecc', '1586504114oyZ4Ra6Z.jpg', '1586504114jXqDRcSS.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 34.41379310344828, 0, '<pre data-hook=\"description\" class=\"_28cEs\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font-family: inherit; word-break: break-word; text-overflow: ellipsis; color: rgb(47, 46, 46); font-size: 15px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit; white-space: normal;\">Our Auto Safety Master Opener is a clever tool to open 5 types of lids cleanly, safely and easily– cans, ring-pulls, fizzy drink pull-tabs, metal crown tops and screw bottle tops.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit; white-space: normal;\">The self-locking Auto Safety function enables easy opening of cans and does not leave any sharp edges behind.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; list-style: circle; font: inherit; white-space: normal;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Automatically attaches itself to cans</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Leaves no sharp edges</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Open items with little effort</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Opens everything cans, bottles, pop and pull tops and more</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Hygienic – opener never touches the contents of the can</li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit; white-space: normal;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px;\">Use &amp; Care</strong></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1em; padding: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; list-style: circle; font: inherit; white-space: normal;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Metal cans: Place opener on top of can and turn knob clockwise until you feel the mechanism engage. Turn the knob clockwise to open the can. After a full circle, you will feel less resistance. Stop – can is open. Turn the knob anti-clockwise until the can is released. Use mini-pliers to lift lid cleanly and easily</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Warning: Don’t cut more than full circle. Over cutting may create burrs or slivers that could cause injury. For domestic use only. Not intended for commercial use.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Ring pulls : Push the hook under the ring, rock backwards and open the can</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Fizzy drink pull tabs: Turn opener over and push the end under the tabe. Press upwards to open the can</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Metal crown tops: Place the opener over the bottle top and turn to the side</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Plastic bottle tops: Place the \'eye\' over the plastic lid and turn to open</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: 0px 0px; font: inherit;\">Wipe clean with damp cloth</li></ul></pre>', NULL, '<br>', 1, 29, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Physical', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2020-04-09 23:34:48', '2020-06-10 14:29:47', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, NULL),
