(506, 'SKUDNO01', 'normal', NULL, 45, 30, 35, NULL, NULL, 'Nano One Treatment Cleansing Gel', 'nano-one-treatment-cleansing-gel-skudno01', '1588229676PUjTTFo7.jpg', '1588229676okXkHg8S.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 26.20689655172414, 0, '<div>Product Description:</div><div>Breakthrough 5 in 1 makeup remover, deep cleanse, gentle exfoliation, purifying and protection treatment cleansing gel suitable for daily cleanse</div><div><br></div><div>Makeup Remover – normal, water proof makeup</div><div>Deep Cleansing – all skin type</div><div>Gentle Exfoliate – face, neck, body (armpit, elbow, inner thigh, butt cleavage, knee)</div><div>Purifying Mask – detox &amp; purifying</div><div>Protection – antioxidants</div><div>Nano One Treatment Cleansing Gel is a magical 5 Action makeup remover, deep cleanser, gentle exfoliant that purifies and protect skin without damaging skin barrier. Incorporated with Nano Technology, it speeds and effectively penetrate and dislodge dirt, impurities or residues, dead cells, traces of makeup and gradually fading off yellow pigment under skin if any. Blackheads, whiteheads and acne formation is under control when pores are purified and cleared.</div><div><br></div><div>PRECAUTIONS:</div><div>Ensure both hands and face are dry</div><div>Avoid wound and inflamed skin</div><div>Rinse with lots of water if the gel accidently get into the eyes</div><div>&nbsp;“Small little balls’ will form on skin with dead cells, residue, dirt and traces of makeup</div><div>Can be applied on oily chest, back, elbow and heel. Excess dead cells will be removed effectively, achieving whitening effect</div><div>Skin with thicker stratum corneum (dead cells), please be advised to use Nano One Treatment Cleansing Gel day and night for the initial 3 – 14 days (adjust accordingly between individual)</div><div>Suitable for normal skin, oily skin, combination skin and dry skin. Use once daily at night 8. For sensitive skin, use 1 – 3 times weekly. (adjust accordingly between individual)</div><div>Not suitable to apply on extreme sensitive skin except on area with thicker stratum corneum (dead cells)</div><div> </div><div>DIRECTIONS</div><div>(Ensuring both hands and face are dry), pump 3-5 ‘pump’ of Nano One Treatment Cleansing Gel onto palm. Spread evenly onto entire face and leave on for the gel to work for 3-5 seconds. Using circular movement, work through the entire face for 1 minute until gel turns into ‘small little balls’. Add on additional Nano One Treatment Cleansing Gel when necessary to facilitate a smooth circular movement. You will see dead cells, residue, dirt and traces of makeup dislodge from facial pores, turning into ‘small little balls’. Rinse off thoroughly with water and pat dry.</div><div><br></div><div>INGREDIENTS:</div><div>Aqua, Cetrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Carbomer, Glycereth-26, Phynoexyethanol (and) Triethylene Glycol, Polysorbate 20, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract (GreenTea)</div>', 20, '<span style=\"text-align: center;\">Price is INCLUSIVE of delivery charges of $10.</span><br style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">No refund/exchange/return.</span><br>', 1, 17, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '3-5 days', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Physical', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2020-04-29 09:54:54', '2020-06-08 04:45:12', 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, NULL, 53),
